---
import '../styles/global.css';

const pageTitle = "A propos";

const identity = {
  firstName: "Sarah",
  country: "Canada",
  occupation: "Technical Writer",
  hobbies: ["photography", "birdwatching", "baseball"],
};

const skills = ["HTML", "CSS", "JavaScript", "React", "Astro", "Writing Docs"];

const happy = true;
const finished = false;
const goal = 3;

const skillColor = "blue";
const fontWeight = "bold";
const textCase = "uppercase";
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{pageTitle}</title>
	</head>
	<body>
        <a href="/">home</a>
        <a href="/about">à propos</a>
		<a href="/blog">blog</a>
		<h1>{pageTitle}</h1>
        <h2>et de celui de mon site Astro</h2>
        <p>Je travaille sur le tuto d'introduction d'Astro. C'est la deuxième page de mon site web, et la première que j'écris moi-même</p>
        <p>Je mettrai à jour le site au fur et à mesure que j'avancerai dans le tuto, donc sureveille ce qui se passe et comment se passe mon aventure!</p>
		
		<p>Here are a few facts about me:</p>
		<ul>
		  <li>My name is {identity.firstName}.</li>
		  <li>I live in {identity.country} and I work as a {identity.occupation}.</li>
		  {identity.hobbies.length >= 2 && 
		    <li>Two of my hobbies are: {identity.hobbies[0]} and {identity.hobbies[1]}</li>
		  } 
		</ul>
		<p>My skills are:</p>
		<ul>
		  {skills.map((skill) => <li class="skill">{skill}</li>)}
		</ul>

		{happy && <p>I am happy to be learning Astro!</p>}

		{finished && <p>I finished this tutorial!</p>}

		{goal === 3 ? <p>My goal is to finish in 3 days.</p> : <p>My goal is not 3 days.</p>}

		
	</body>
	<style define:vars={{skillColor, fontWeight, textCase}}>
	h1 {
	  color: purple;
	  font-size: 4rem;
	}
	.skill {
		color: var(--skillColor);
		font-weight: var(--fontWeight);
 	   	text-transform: var(--textCase);
	}
	</style>
</html>